- I know! I heard you!

14:39.797 --> 14:42.088
It's just that I just sold
a screenplay,

14:42.088 --> 14:43.838
and the girl that gave me
Chlamydia,

14:43.838 --> 14:45.797
is gonna be my girlfriend.

14:45.797 --> 14:47.713
- Hooray!
- Yeah. Come here!

14:48.880 --> 14:51.672
- Uh...
- (Kiss) Ahh!

14:51.672 --> 14:59.547
♪♪♪

14:59.547 --> 15:02.213
(Phone chimes)

15:02.213 --> 15:04.297
- (Chuckles) Slacklining?

15:05.880 --> 15:08.880
You crazy kids.
- What's that?

15:08.880 --> 15:10.588
- Oh here, check it out.

15:13.547 --> 15:15.338
- Who is this creature?

15:15.338 --> 15:17.755
- Oh, that's just a girl
I've been seein'.

15:19.380 --> 15:21.047
- Girl?

15:22.838 --> 15:24.713
You're seeing other people?

15:24.713 --> 15:27.588
- Oh, well I just thought
we were, you know, casual.

15:27.588 --> 15:29.547
- Casual. (Chuckles)

15:29.547 --> 15:31.380
You live in my home!

15:31.380 --> 15:33.505
- Yeah, I just thought--
- Frankie,

15:33.505 --> 15:35.922
I am finding this
very disrespectful.

15:35.922 --> 15:37.755
♪♪♪

15:37.755 --> 15:40.880
♪ Took your head outta
my hands ♪

15:42.963 --> 15:48.172
♪ And left your empty shell
on the shoreline ♪

15:53.255 --> 15:55.047
<i> (Footsteps thud)</i>

15:57.672 --> 16:01.088
- Well, well, well!
What is this?

16:04.130 --> 16:06.380
- It's a video of Alice
and Giroux.

16:06.380 --> 16:09.380
- Huh. You set up the Go Pro.
- Yes.

16:10.797 --> 16:13.130
- But Anne, that is an invasion
of her privacy.

16:13.130 --> 16:15.838
- Lionel! I feel bad enough
already.

16:15.838 --> 16:17.713
Now would you please
press play,

16:17.713 --> 16:20.338
because I cannot bring myself
to do it.

16:20.338 --> 16:21.630
(Clicks remote button)

16:22.630 --> 16:24.422
(Silence)

16:27.838 --> 16:29.922
- Take off your shirt!

16:32.172 --> 16:34.380
Sit on the bed.

16:35.922 --> 16:37.713
Put this on!

16:39.880 --> 16:41.588
<i> Put this in your mouth.</i>

16:41.588 --> 16:43.130
- No!

16:43.130 --> 16:46.005
- Is this a sock?
- Put the sock in your mouth!

16:46.005 --> 16:49.130
- Please, please don't do it.
Alice: Do it!

16:49.130 --> 16:53.005
♪♪♪

16:53.005 --> 16:56.713
<i> You've been kidnapped,</i>
<i>now say goodbye to your family.</i>

16:56.713 --> 16:58.255
(Stunned silence)

17:01.963 --> 17:03.547
(Footsteps thud)

17:08.922 --> 17:11.547
(Muffled heavy metal music
plays)

17:12.880 --> 17:14.088
(Door opens)

17:15.172 --> 17:17.213
(Heavy metal music plays)

17:18.297 --> 17:20.255
- Hey!
- Hey.

17:20.255 --> 17:22.713
- Oh, um, roller skating's
not 'til like...

17:22.713 --> 17:26.713
- Um, the thing is Juniper is...
is I don't think I can--

17:26.713 --> 17:29.005
- Hey, hands off my sausages,
Johnny!

17:29.005 --> 17:31.005
Defrost your own pack!

17:31.005 --> 17:32.505
(Microwave door slams)
Sorry, what's up?

17:32.505 --> 17:36.922
Are you sick or something?
- No, I'm not sick. Uh...

17:36.922 --> 17:39.505
I just don't think we should
hang out anymore.

17:39.505 --> 17:41.172
- I thought you came here
to hang out?

17:41.172 --> 17:43.005
- Oh... well I just thought
I owed it to you,

17:43.005 --> 17:45.422
to like tell you where
I was at and not disappear.

17:45.422 --> 17:48.755
- Why?
- 'Cause I think that's what--

17:48.755 --> 17:50.463
(Hard thud,
silverware clatters)

17:50.463 --> 17:52.547
- Seriously, Johnny, fuck off!

17:52.547 --> 17:55.463
All right, well,
take it easy, I guess.

17:55.463 --> 17:57.588
- Listen, Juniper,
I just want you to know

17:57.588 --> 18:00.130
how much I've learned from--
- Johnny, what the fuck?!

18:00.130 --> 18:02.047
Sorry, I gotta go and hog tie
this motherfucker.

18:02.047 --> 18:03.797
- Of course... you do.
- Okay?

18:03.797 --> 18:05.547
- Yup.
(Door slams shut)

18:05.547 --> 18:12.130
♪♪♪

18:12.130 --> 18:14.172
<i> Anne: Hey you.</i>

18:14.172 --> 18:15.672
- Hi.

18:17.297 --> 18:18.547
- Have a seat,

18:18.547 --> 18:20.505
there's something I wanna talk
to you about.

18:20.505 --> 18:21.838
- That's funny,

18:21.838 --> 18:24.505
'cause there's something I
wanna talk to you about.

18:24.505 --> 18:25.797
(Camera thuds)

18:27.130 --> 18:28.630
- Shit.

18:28.630 --> 18:30.630
- Is this what you call privacy?

18:30.630 --> 18:32.755
- How did you even...
- If you're going to film me,

18:32.755 --> 18:34.755
be a bit more subtle about it.

18:34.755 --> 18:37.422
I hope you liked our hostage
video.

18:37.422 --> 18:40.338
- Whoa, Alice... stop!
Have a seat, please.

18:44.255 --> 18:47.172
I'm sorry, okay, you're right.

18:47.172 --> 18:49.172
You deserve to be respected.

18:50.255 --> 18:52.838
But the privilege of privacy
comes with a few rules.

18:52.838 --> 18:54.380
If you wanna be able to close
your door,

18:54.380 --> 18:55.880
then you have to be honest

18:55.880 --> 18:57.380
about what's happening
behind it.

18:57.380 --> 18:59.338
- I am being honest with you.

18:59.338 --> 19:02.505
- Then why go through the
trouble of making a video?

19:02.505 --> 19:05.380
Look, I'm just proposing
a trade-off here, okay?

19:05.380 --> 19:08.713
I give you some freedoms,
and you give me transparency.

19:08.713 --> 19:10.130
- Okay.

19:10.130 --> 19:12.297
- Do you know what
that word means?

19:12.297 --> 19:14.713
- You want me to have
a see-through door?

19:14.713 --> 19:17.172
- (Sighs)

19:17.172 --> 19:19.047
Alice, I...

19:20.422 --> 19:23.547
I know that you think
you got it all figured out,

19:23.547 --> 19:25.422
but you gotta trust me
when I say

19:25.422 --> 19:27.672
that there's some curveballs
coming and...

19:29.588 --> 19:31.547
they can be kinda scary.

19:31.547 --> 19:32.838
I just want...

19:33.838 --> 19:35.880
I would like to be
your sounding board.

19:35.880 --> 19:37.880
Okay, that doesn't mean that
you have to think what I think,

19:37.880 --> 19:39.338
I just...

19:39.338 --> 19:42.130
I would just like to be
in the know.

19:42.130 --> 19:44.130
Does that make sense?

19:45.338 --> 19:46.713
- Yeah.

19:49.588 --> 19:51.172
- Okay. Good.

19:56.213 --> 19:58.338
So...

19:58.338 --> 20:00.172
tell me what was going on

20:00.172 --> 20:02.338
before I installed the Go Pro
in your room.

20:08.505 --> 20:10.422
- I was playing doctor.

20:11.880 --> 20:14.380
- Right. And...

20:14.380 --> 20:16.005
and what does that mean?

20:17.130 --> 20:19.963
There's no judgment.
You can trust me.

20:19.963 --> 20:22.088
♪ And sad as hell ♪

20:22.088 --> 20:24.088
♪ And I feel like giving up ♪

20:24.088 --> 20:27.088
- (Sighs) So... this is what
happened.

20:29.297 --> 20:31.505
♪ Can you hold my heart ♪

20:33.255 --> 20:35.255
♪ I know you... ♪

20:36.505 --> 20:40.755
<i> Dad: Katie, it's Dad. You</i>
<i>there? I thought you picked up.</i>

20:40.755 --> 20:42.630
(Engine revs,
crunching mashing sound)

20:42.630 --> 20:45.547
<i> Your mother and I were</i>
<i> wondering about dinner</i>
<i> next weekend.</i>

20:45.547 --> 20:47.255
(Engine revs, car thuds)

20:47.255 --> 20:50.172
<i> Anyway, love you, kid.</i>
<i> Keep at it.</i>

20:51.213 --> 20:54.463
<i>Shit... I just stepped in shit.</i>

20:57.713 --> 20:58.963
(Engine revs)

21:00.047 --> 21:03.047
♪♪♪
